content management system with core php
==============================
 * This source code was developed as a practise project 
 
Notes
=====

   Task Manager is a simple cms where users can register and add a task they aspire to achieve.
   Administrators can make other users to become an admin.
   This project  follows the Model View and Controller(MVC) architecture.
   Yes (: my first object oriented programming project
   
   files includes
   
   <app> - contains all the php files
   <css> - contains the stylesheet
   <js>  - javascript files
   <sql> - The sql files for database
   index.php - index page
   readme.md - info about this app
   
